# Site Tags

This script returns an ordered list of tags.

Parameters:

- `initial`: An optional character to filter the tags

The resulting array is returned in a variable `site__tags`.

## Input parameters

- `initial`: {{ include.initial }}


{% assign site__tags = site.data.arrays.empty %}

{% for tags in site.tags %}

	{% assign tag = tags | first %}

	{% if include.initial %}
		{% assign initial = tag | downcase | split: '' %}
		{% if include.initial != initial[0] %}{% continue %}{% endif %}
	{% endif %}

	{% assign site__tags = site__tags | push: tag %}

{% endfor %}

{% assign site__tags = site__tags | sort %}

{% assign initial = null %}
{% assign tag = null %}

